        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "As a developer, I've spent countless hours wrestling with chat implementations—until I discovered CometChat. This SDK lets you add real-time text, voice, and video communication to any app in record time. Imagine slashing your development timeline from weeks to hours. If you're looking to enhance user engagement without the headache, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "sign up for CometChat's free plan",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and see the magic firsthand. It's a tool that has transformed how I build apps, and I'm excited to share a step-by-step tutorial to get you started.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
