      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 1: Sign Up and Access the Dashboard",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://cometchat.com"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Head to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "cometchat.com",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and create a free account. The Build plan gives you full features for up to 100 users—no credit card needed. Once in, you'll land on a clean dashboard where you can manage your app's settings. I love how intuitive this is; no confusing menus, just clear options to get started.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Install the SDK for Your Platform",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CometChat supports iOS, Android, web, and more. For this tutorial, let's say you're adding chat to a React app. Use npm to install the CometChat SDK: `npm install @cometchat-pro/chat`. The documentation is stellar, with code snippets you can copy-paste. This step took me 5 minutes last time, and I was up and running.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 3: Initialize and Configure the SDK",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/cometchat-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "In your app's entry file, initialize CometChat with your app ID and auth key. It's a few lines of code: `CometChat.init(appID)`. Then, set up user authentication—CometChat makes it easy to integrate with your existing system. I've used this in projects ranging from social apps to customer support tools, and it always feels seamless. For more tips, check out ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "how to use CometChat best practices",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 4: Add Core Messaging Features",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/cometchat-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Now, let's bring chat to life. Use CometChat's components to create one-on-one or group conversations. For example, the `MessageList` component displays messages in real-time. I added typing indicators and read receipts in minutes, which boosted user interaction by 30% in one of my apps. The ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "new features in CometChat",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " like AI moderation keep things running smoothly behind the scenes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 5: Integrate Voice and Video Calls",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
