        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-cometchat"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want to go beyond text? Enable voice and video calls with the `Calling` module. It's as simple as calling `CometChat.startCall()`. I've built customer support apps where users can escalate from chat to video with one click—this integration saved weeks of development time. Explore ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "why CometChat stands out",
            "marks": [
              "l5"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for its reliability in high-traffic scenarios.",
            "marks": []
